PUT 'QUOTE CONVERT' AT THE TOP OFYOUR APPLESOFT PROGRAMS TO EMBEDQUOTATION MARKS WITHIN QUOTEDSTRINGS. AFTER THE LINE EXECUTES; @SYMBOLS WILL BE DISPLAYED ASQUOTATION MARKS. SO;WHENEVER YOU WISH TO PUT A QUOTATIONMARK IN A PRINT STATEMENT; TYPE A @SYMBOL INSTEAD.USE 'PR#0' TO RESTORE THE CORRECTDISPLAY OF THE @ SYMBOL. OUTPUT TOTHE PRINTER IS NOT AFFECTED.